 21:38","userId":"zq0504032","userName":"满舰饰假子","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">树洞酱</span> 说: 真好啊 <br>科三让你们自己练不怕出事吗</q></div>我学车的时候，教练车是个改造过的破普桑，副驾座位上有一个刹车，别的没了<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/36/213658.jpg","floor":"#12-3","id":"1416970","time":"2019-1-30 22:13","userId":"213658","userName":"神户猪肉","userSign":"","message":"我们当时3200报的，还嫌贵了。。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/38/29/382951.jpg","floor":"#12-4","id":"1416988","time":"2019-1-30 22:52","userId":"382951","userName":"树洞酱","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">满舰饰假子</span> 说: 我学车的时候，教练车是个改造过的破普桑，副驾座位上有一个刹车，别的没了</q></div>不应该是这样么<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><br>还应该有什么么<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/64/216493.jpg","floor":"#13","id":"1417220","time":"2019-1-31 12:35","userId":"216493","userName":"padorax","userSign":"(戯言なんだよ)","message":"教练最好找亲戚朋友认识的，不然很麻烦<br>不过未来学车应该不需要教练了或者根本就需要学车了（","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/02/60/26024.jpg","floor":"#14","id":"1417235","time":"2019-1-31 13:05","userId":"everpcpc","userName":"蜜瓜改二@五月病🍭","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q>不够熟练，有几个地方出了问题，挂了。</q></div>","sub":[]}]